Library is currently fully public (`/library` → no auth check anywhere).

#### [MODIFY] [PublicNavbar.tsx](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/components/layout/PublicNavbar.tsx)
- Hide `E-Library` nav item when user is not logged in.

#### [MODIFY] [library/page.tsx](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/%28public%29/library/page.tsx)
- Add [useSession()](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/tests/unit/components/navbar.test.tsx#13-14) at the top of [PublicLibrary](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/%28public%29/library/page.tsx#75-396).
