---

### Feature 2 — Admin Approval Gate

**Flow:**
1. Student registers (email or Google) → `status: 'pending'` in DB.
2. Student sees a **"Pending Approval"** screen after registration/login. Cannot access dashboard.
3. Admin sees a list of pending students and can **Approve** or **Reject** each one.
4. On approval → `status: 'active'` → student can now access dashboard.
5. On rejection → `status: 'rejected'` → student sees rejection message.

#### [MODIFY] [User.ts](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/models/User.ts)
- Add `'pending'` and `'rejected'` to the `status` enum.
- Change default from `'active'` to `'pending'` for new users.
- Admins stay `'active'` always — so the register API must explicitly set admin accounts to active.

#### [MODIFY] [auth.ts](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/lib/auth.ts)
- Add `status` field to JWT and Session.
- Block login for `rejected` users with a clear error message.

#### [MODIFY] [next-auth.d.ts](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/types/next-auth.d.ts)
- Add `status` to User, Session, and JWT types.

#### [MODIFY] [middleware.ts](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/middleware.ts)
- Add check: if `token.status === 'pending'` or `'rejected'` → redirect to `/pending-approval` instead of dashboard.
- Add `/pending-approval` to matcher.

#### [NEW] `src/app/pending-approval/page.tsx`
- Beautiful page shown to students whose account is pending admin review.
- Shows college logo, status message, and email.
- If `status === 'rejected'` → shows rejection message.

#### [MODIFY] [register/route.ts](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/api/auth/register/route.ts)
- Set `status: 'pending'` on new email/password registrations.

#### [MODIFY] [auth.ts signIn callback](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/lib/auth.ts)
- Set `status: 'pending'` on new Google users created via signIn callback.

#### [NEW] `src/app/api/admin/users/approve/route.ts`
- `PATCH /api/admin/users/approve` — set `status: 'active'` for a user by ID.
- `PATCH /api/admin/users/reject` — set `status: 'rejected'` for a user by ID.
- Admin role required.

#### [MODIFY] [admin/students/page.tsx](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/%28admin%29/admin/students/page.tsx)
- Add a **"Pending Approvals"** tab at the top showing students with `status: 'pending'`.
- Each row has **Approve** ✅ and **Reject** ❌ buttons.
- After action, row moves out of pending list.

